name: 奥尚·拉米雷斯
name_full: 奥尚·拉米雷斯 Oshún Ramirez
introduction: Oshún Ramirez was born in Los Angeles, California in 2008. Oshún has booked national commercials for Acura, My Little Pony, and Salad Gig. As a voice actress she is known for multiple episodes of Disney XD's Future-Worm, Mickey and the Roadster Racers, and Tig & Seek. She does ADR work which includes the Netflix series Jessica Jones. She has been fencing since the age of 5 and enjoys tennis, swimming, skateboarding, figure skating, and plays flute.
